2000px" /></p><p>据报道，由于好莱坞持续罢工，2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/emmys">艾美奖颁奖典礼</a>将被推迟。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-will-the-hollywood-actors-strike-last-3473291">好莱坞演员的罢工会持续多久？</a></strong></li></ul><p>第 75 届黄金时段艾美奖颁奖典礼定于 9 月 18 日星期一在洛杉矶孔雀剧院举行。</p><p>现在， <em><a href="https://variety.com/2023/tv/news/emmys-airdate-actors-writers-strike-1235681067/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《综艺》</a></em>报道称，业内持续的编剧和演员罢工导致组织者推迟了原定日期。</p><p>该报告补充说，他们目前正在寻找颁奖的替代日期， <em>《Variety》</em>暗示日期为 2024 年 1 月。 </p><figure id="attachment_3450292" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3450292" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3450292" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg" alt="继任结局" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Shiv-succession-finale-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3450292" class="wp-caption-text"> 《继承之战》以 27 项提名领跑 2023 年艾美奖提名。图片来源：HBO</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/succession"><em>《继承之战》</em></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/succession-the-last-of-us-lead-2023-emmy-nominations-3467960">获得 2023 年艾美奖提名最多，共获得 27 项提名</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-last-of-us"><em>《最后生还者》</em></a>以 24 项提名落后。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-white-lotus"><em>《白莲花》</em></a